                     <interp inst="t17111205-11-off50" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               privately stealing 24 Ounces of Hair value 3 l.
            </rs> the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17111205-11-victim68" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Hains
                  <interp inst="t17111205-11-victim68" type="surname" value="Hains"></interp>
